TermiPod is a derivative work of MuxPod. It has been substantially
modified and extended. The original MuxPod provided SSH connectivity
and basic tmux session viewing for Android. TermiPod adds cross-platform
support (iOS/iPadOS), a redesigned input system with action bar profiles
and compose bar, structured agent snippets, SSH ProxyJump and SOCKS5
proxy support, SFTP file transfer, navigation pad with gesture controls,
raw PTY mode, custom keyboard, key overlay, help/onboarding, deep linking,
auto-extend scrollback, and other features.

For a list of changes, see the git history of this repository.
